Producer: Katie Holmes, Jordan Yale Levine, Jordan Beckerman, Jesse Korman, Shaun Sanghani, Mark Maxey
Production Co: Rolling Pictures, SSS Entertainment, Lafayette Pictures, IFC Productions, Yale Productions, Lucky 13 Productions
Synopsis: An adaptation of Kathleen Tessaro's novel of the same name, Rare Objects is a story about friendship that centers around a young woman who reclaims her own sense of self through her journey of self discovery that involves a new job, new friends and healing.
Title: Rare Objects
